      <title>波音观察人士称，可能的股权出售或可避免降级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/boeing-watchers-say-possible-equity-sale-could-avert-downgrade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师和市场参与者表示，如果波音公司决定筹集股本，这将有助于该公司至少在几个月内避免评级下调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/boeing-watchers-say-possible-equity-sale-could-avert-downgrade</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 15:39:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
